A Maxima package with some common 3D homogenous transformation functionality
(e.g. rotations, translations, etc.). 

The actual package is the file "homogenous_transformation.mac".
Additionally, a simple unit test and demo batch script "ht_test.mac"
is included. To execute it, enter the following statement in Maxima:
  batch("ht_test.mac")$

For more information, see Doxygen style comments in the package file
"homogenous_transformation.mac".

The package is licenced under the Apache 2.0 license. See LICENSE.txt and
http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
for more details.

The author of the package is Jernej Kovacic (jkovacic AT gmail DOT com).
